<h1><p>Strategies</p></h1>
<p><b>There are always other ways to say things!</b></p>

<p class="linespace"></p>
<p>Don't panic if you can't remember a word, or if you feel you are stuck for words.</p>

<p class="linespace"></p>
<p>Remember the following expressions:</p>

<p color="#0000FF">I'm not sure what it's called, but it is / looks like / is used for ..."</p>
<p color="#0000FF">"I've forgotten what it is in English, but ..."</p>
<p color="#0000FF">"It's similar to ... , but I don't remember the word."</p>

<p class="linespace"></p>
<p><b>We all forget words sometimes. It happens in natural conversations. Don't let it bother you!</b></p>
